---
title: Quick Lemon & Prawn Fusilli with Chilli Flakes & Bacon Bits
description: A seafood pasta feels fancy without even trying and we think a squeeze of zesty lemon juice with these prawns is enough to
earn a five star rating for this fusilli dish. We’ll let you be the judge.

*We’ve replaced the orecchiette in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
